Intro to Capybara Tests

In this lesson, we'll discuss integration testing with Capybara.
OBJECTIVES
Define an integration test and compare it to unit and controller tests.
Use Capybara for integration tests by including it in the testing environment.
Use the Capybara methods visit and page when writing tests.
Read a Capybara test of response HTML.
Read a Capybara test that interacts with HTML.
Read a Capybara test that submits an HTML form.

